7 PARTS IN A PUBLIC PLACE TO MEMBERS OF THE OPPOSITE SEX OR THE OPPOSITE SEX ASSIGNED
8 OBSERVED AT BIRTH TO THE PERSON WITH THE INTENT TO VIOLATE THE DIGNITY OF A PERSON IN
